      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start, but it's a bit too generic. I need it to be more specific about the \"radicalism\" part to really get the crowd fired up. Can you add a section that specifically calls out how these progressive policies are actually destroying the foundation of the home and why they're a threat to our way of life? Use some stronger language to show why these ideas are wrong.",
